column5: I blinked and missed the first half of your race! That was quick!

column7: Your speed was impressive, but next time, try not to leave the spectators in the dust... literally!
Way to stay focused during the race! Keep that mindset for the next one.

column6: 56th Holly-Duane Raffin Festival of Races (D1 JV Boys)
column7: Great run! If only we could bottle that energy for Monday mornings.
